[2026-05-28 23:18:50] local.INFO: Diagnosis Step Output {"diagnosis":{"confidence":0.9,"estimated_price_max":3000,"estimated_price_min":1500,"issue_type":"pipe_leak","recommended_service":"Leak detection and pipe repair","summary":"There's a pipe leaking under your sink. This typically indicates a loose fitting, a worn-out washer, or a corroded pipe section. It's important to address this quickly to prevent water damage and mold growth. A professional plumber can identify the exact source of the leak and carry out the necessary repair.","urgency":"medium","provider":"gemini","model":"gemini-2.5-flash"}} 
