[2026-05-29 00:24:45] local.INFO: Diagnosis Step Output {"diagnosis":{"confidence":0.8,"estimated_price_max":4500,"estimated_price_min":1500,"issue_type":"pipe_leak","recommended_service":"Pipe leak inspection and repair","summary":"A pipe leaking under the sink requires prompt inspection and repair to prevent further water damage. The estimated cost covers labor and potential minor part replacement (e.g., fittings, P-trap). The exact cost will depend on the specific source and severity of the leak, as well as the type of pipe material involved. For a more precise estimate, please provide details on the exact location of the leak (e.g., at a joint, on the pipe body, near the drain) and the type of sink (e.g., kitchen, bathroom).","urgency":"medium","provider":"gemini","model":"gemini-2.5-flash"}} 
